dialogueLines: You can't come up here. This is private property, owned by Sad Smaltman.
Yes, I can play music. I'm a clarinet player, but I haven't played in years.
Ever since I got this new job, I haven't had the time.
You really think it's a good idea? Alright, let's groove!
Wait! My lunch break is over!
I've gotta get back to work!
Wait... You can get me out of this? Alright, come on!
